{"tid":1052203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跳舞遭人取笑後動武　劉馬車涉公眾地方打鬥","createTime":"2019-03-08T06:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T03:23:00.000Z","uid":2748,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"631717c815516556cd6a50d21657508102819530","tid":1052203,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190308/photo/bkn-20190308124641422-0308_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190308131231\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190308%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190308124641422-0308_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190308131231&h=715a8891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  在網上自稱「劉馬車」的男子劉駿軒今年初在天水圍跳舞時，遭一名路過的青年取笑，雙方頓起爭執，並疑繼而動武，兩人被控在公眾地方打鬥罪，案件今(8日)在屯門法院提訊，青年獲准以2000港元守行為一年，劉則毋須答辯，保釋至5月3日再訊，讓辯方索閱文件。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n  兩名被告為劉駿軒(22歲，無業)和陳耀東(24歲，售貨員)，控罪指他們於今年1月5日，在天水圍銀座廣場非法打鬥。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n  針對陳的案情指，陳當晚11時途經上址時見劉在跳舞，陳出言取笑，兩人起爭執並打起來，最終一同被捕，警誡下劉指陳先動手，他只是自衞；陳則指劉先動手。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"b53c66536044d2c710069d5d5d2fb4569e05f3ee","tid":1052203,"uid":40470,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:48:42.000Z","msg":"老師，係佢打我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係，係佢打我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e7a59da16b85c4f29661fbbfa24c1fd58a0ef6","tid":1052203,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:50:47.000Z","msg":"以為係撩人條女"},{"pid":"c63e2ad0069c78b1cbc0b00203d7762be6499078","tid":1052203,"uid":818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:51:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dddbb08868c7a88e2136b04512338afe2307b6b","tid":1052203,"uid":186997,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T06:53:35.000Z","msg":"之前睇佢啲所謂跳舞片見佢跳到好似